I had some issues with the alpha client not being able to patch. It would scan all the files, staying at 0%, but never go up and eventually tell me that I had to retry the update. After a few attempts I just decided to Uninstall/reinstall. Well now I cant re-download the alpha client. ggez {{item:3070}} {{item:3070}}


UPDATE:
Now when i click "Launch" on the Legacy client i get a message to reinstall my Alpha client. so i can't play at all. le sigh.
